### 1. Start Agent Flow
POST http://localhost:8080/agent
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "docId": "spring-boot-qa",
  "prompt": "Summarize exception handling in Spring Boot and email it to HR",
  "recipientEmail": "hr@company.com",
  "topK": 5
}

> {%
    // 🔥 capture sessionId from response
    client.global.set("sessionId", response.body.sessionId);
%}

###

### 2. Continue - Change Recipient
